text: Saiful Alam (born 28 October 1968) is a Bangladeshi sport shooter. He competed in the 10 m air rifle event at the 1996 Summer Olympics, Alam scored 581 points and finished in 33rd position. ==References== Category:1968 births Category:Living people Category:ISSF rifle shooters Category:Bangladeshi male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Bangladesh Category:Shooters at the 1996 Summer Olympics
